Welcome to Canvas Max, developed by Appycron Interactive e.K.. We respect the privacy of our users and are committed to protecting it through our compliance with this policy.
Data We Collect
We only collect your purchase history and anonymous statistical data related to crash frequency and feature usage. This data helps us understand the performance of our app and areas for improvement. This statistical data cannot be used to identify individual users.
Where Your Data is Stored
All documents or data you create or save within Infinite Pro are stored exclusively on your device or your iCloud, based on your settings and preferences. We do not have access to, nor do we store any of your documents or data on our servers.
Third-Party Services
Our app does not integrate or utilize any third-party services that may collect personal data, beyond the native iCloud storage provided by Apple, which users have the option to utilize.
Childrenâ€™s Privacy
While Infinite Pro is designed for users of all ages, we do not knowingly collect any personal information from children under the age of 13.
Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may occasionally update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated Effective Date. Users are encouraged to periodically review this policy for any changes.
